# What is the significance of Lyman for the Russian military?

## Summary
The retreat of Russian forces from Lyman is a major embarrassment for Moscow and a strategic loss for Russia. Lyman is a key supply hub on the western edge of Ukraines Donbas region, where Russia has concentrated its military campaign for months. Russian forces have used it to supply operations to the east since capturing Lyman in the spring. The retreat from Lyman will significantly affect Russias ability to supply, resupply and move its forces all along the forward line of conflict.

